## Development

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourname/weatherwhisper.git
cd weatherwhisper
python -m venv venv && source venv/bin/activate
pip install -e ".[dev]"
pre-commit install
```

Run the CLI from source:

```bash
python -m weatherwhisper current "London"
```

Tests:

```bash
pytest
```

